node.text: @a.sp00nful why u keep changing name??? U trying to avoid pple???? Haha

Dairy free Cempadek Cake : very moist and natural sweetness from the fruit... if u r a fan of cempadek, BUY! Its Limited Edition!!!(banana cake texture) every bite has cempadek!!!
Lontong sayur: the Rempah coconut gravy is very rich. My folks love it.
Sate Ayam : love the satay sauce, not the usual kind. I think This is some lemongrass and lime in it..the ayam sate has this grilled flavour. Would be perfect if they have other meat choices too.
Had a Very good lunch w the family!
